/* 
List of attributes (can also be found on the guide, but its more detailed):
  number_of_objects
  number_of_groups
  set_place_for_every_player
  set_scaling_by_map_size
  set_scaling_to_player_number
  min_distance_to_players
  max_distance_to_players
  set_tight_grouping
  set_loose_grouping
  group_placement_radius
  group_variance
  set_gaia_object_only
  min_distance_group_placement
  temp_min_distance_group_placement
  max_distance_to_other_zones
  terrain_to_place_on
  resource_delta                  increase or decrease the amount of res that an object has. +100 to deer will m ake deer have an extra 100 food, -11 will make it have 100 less food
  place_on_specific_land_id       only works if there is separation bw the player and the land_id
*/


